      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "$34,900 - Good, well-kept vehicle that shows nicely overall and should make a strong choice for someone looking for a solid used car. It runs and drives well, presents cleanly inside and out, and appears to have been cared for, though it is not a mint example. Expect normal light cosmetic wear and age-appropriate signs of use, but overall this is an honest, good-condition vehicle that should satisfy a buyer wanting something presentable and dependable without paying top-of-market money.",
