      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical choice for someone seeking dependable basic transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values utility, simplicity, and strong budget appeal. A solid opportunity for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone looking for inexpensive wheels.",
