    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transport, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. It has the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect at this stage, but it still offers a lot of value for the money and could be a smart buy for someone practical. If you\u2019re after something cheap, straightforward, and full of potential, this is well worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project with a strong-running engine, responsive transmission, and a chassis that still feels planted where it counts. Not a showroom car, but it has the kind of mechanical honesty enthusiasts appreciate\u2014starts, moves, and drives with good power delivery, making it an excellent budget daily, backup vehicle, or platform for light restoration. Shows cosmetic wear consistent with age and use, but the core components feel usable and well-sorted for the price. If you want affordable transportation with real potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
